📄✨ AI Portfolio Generator

Turn your resume into a live portfolio site with Python + LLM/NLP magic.
(Supports PDF/TXT → Auto-extraction → Beautiful HTML Portfolio)

🚀 How to Use

Paste your resume path in PDF_TO_TEXT.py → Get CV_EXTRACTED_INFO.txt
Feed the text file to Extracted_info_llm.py → Get structured Extracted_Info.json
Run Final_MakeSite.py → Boom! 🎉 Find your portfolio in Here's_Your_Portfolio_Duh/

🌟 Why This?

Zero manual editing – Resume → Portfolio in 3 steps
LLM + NLP hybrid – Smart extraction (handles messy formats)
Modern HTML/CSS – Clean, mobile-friendly template

⚙️ Tech Stack

Extraction	Generation
Ollama (Llama3)	Jinja2 HTML Templates
spaCy (NLP)	CSS/Bootstrap
Regex (patterns)	Python (backend)

📂 Project Structure
.
├── PDF_TO_TEXT.py          # Step 1: Text extraction (PDF/TXT)
├── Extracted_info_llm.py   # Step 2: LLM data extraction → JSON  
├── Final_MakeSite.py       # Step 3: HTML generator  
├── templates/              # Portfolio HTML/CSS  
└── Here's_Your_Portfolio_Duh/  # Output folder  

💡 Key Features

✅ LLM-Powered Extraction – Better than rule-based NLP for messy resumes
✅ Education/Skills/Projects Detection – No fixed format needed
✅ Open-Source – Customize templates or extraction logic

